If you want to use it on a real server , run install.sh

High Availability cluster
If you want to test in a virtual environment, run install_vm.sh

=======================================================

We are going to configure ha-lvm on a two-node cluster and create Apache, Tomcat and Oracle resources.



======================================================
Real server condition
=====================
2 real server 
CentOS7.9
Pacemaker
2 node cluster
fence_ipmilan
ha-lvm
apache / tomcat / oracle / 
==========================

Test in a virtual environment condition
=======================================
vmware workstation 16
2 vm ( kvm / vbmc )
Pacemaker
2 node cluster
kvm - centos 7.9 / 램 8GB / Cpu가상화 체크 / GUI환경 / disk 100GB
vbmc - centos 7.9 최소설치 / 램 1GB / disk 15GB
kvm - libvirt 설치 및 vm머신 3개 생성 (ha1/ha2/storage)
vbmc - vbmc 인스톨 및 셋팅
ha1 - ha생성
ha1 - fence_ipmilan 
storage - iscsi 생성
ha1 , ha2 - 볼륨확인 및 멀티패스
ha1 - LVM 설정 
ha1 - LVM resource
ha1 - Filesystem resource
ha1 - ping resource
ha1 - apache webserver
ha1 - apache tomcat
ha1 - oracle





